Output vhs/out/_throwaway.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set Theme "Builtin Dark"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1240
Set Height 560
Set Padding 6
Env BB_THEME "dark"
Type "bash vhs/run-bb.sh"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "i"
Sleep 500ms
Type "demo-xy3"
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
Screenshot vhs/out/theme-dark-ok-140.png
Sleep 400ms
